        },
        {
          "username": "Zaair Vasquez",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "114931939745231040323",
          "user_review_count": 45,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJqVN835fdNKanAlZ87a4nfRAKl42eaQVLpeYfND8_o-eELw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Hi Dr. Bard's office made an appointment for in person back in January 2023, they called me to confirm my appointment this morning. After. Confirming my appointment,  her office, manager included then stated that I had to pay 25 dollars so my appointment for tomorrow does not get canceled. Needless to say, I do not recommend you see this doctor as a professional physician. I'm sure she is a nice person, buy first impressions say everything. I will also not be returning to this specialty group after being a patient of them since 2020.\nAmendment:\nAfter reading those 1 star reviews, stay away from this lady at all cost, take it from someone in the medical field, find a doctor that cares about you. Also, her staff are all unprofessional, especially the manager.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURodnQyaDhnRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x8469d5f6b02876e3!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDhvt2h8gE%7C%7C?hl=en",
