          "description": "So greatfull for Dr. Bard! She performed a procedure on me with perfect results.  In my line of work, I can\u2019t afford to have anything other than perfection and Dr. Bard delivered!  She listened to my needs and was very patient with me.  She\u2019s the only one who has been able to perform this procedure on me without real pain, a gentle touch.  I\u2019ve been to many Dermatologists, and now I have one I would like to keep with Dr. Bard.  Highly highly recommended!",
